title_zh: 用 Stitch 打造的 AI 导航站
description_en: A curated AI navigation site redesigned from inspiration to production.
description_zh: 从灵感网站到上线的 AI 导航站。
detailed_content_en: We wanted a beautiful AI navigation website. After discovering mad.ac and loving its layout, we asked Stitch to generate a similar frontend experience. We then copied the code and used Cursor to implement the full site quickly. The result is a clean, modern directory with fast iteration and a strong visual identity.
detailed_content_zh: 我们想做一个好看的 AI 导航网址。看到 mad.ac 后很喜欢它的设计风格，于是让 Stitch 生成相似的前端设计，再把代码复制给 Cursor 实现完整页面。最终快速做出一个视觉统一、更新效率高的 AI 导航站。
